      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model employed for titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) screw and UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate per ASTM F1717 protocol. Elastic assumption validated against experimental load-displacement curves: yield onset observed at ~1840 N mean; model captures pre-yield regime (primary QoI region) with high fidelity. Post-yield behavior modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening (tangent modulus from coupon testing). Geometric nonlinearity (large deformation) included. Contact between screw and rod modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation. Model form uncertainty quantified as ±4% on stiffness QoI via comparison with higher-fidelity plasticity models on subset of cases. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
